# Documentation

| Kind | Location |
|------|----------|
| Index | [docs/README.md](../docs/README.md) |
| Workflow | [docs/github-workflow.md](../docs/github-workflow.md) |
| Changes | [CHANGELOG.md](../CHANGELOG.md), [documenting-changes.md](../docs/documenting-changes.md) |
| Agent rules | `.cursor/rules/*.mdc` |

Update docs in the **same PR** when altering:

- Settings tabs or preference keys
- Environment variables or config file layout
- Supported services or API routes
- Docker / Unraid deployment steps

For non-trivial behaviour (merge logic, refresh, theme), add a short **Behaviour** note in the relevant doc — not only UI steps.

Issue and PR must reference doc updates in their checklist.
